  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"traditional\"><p id=\"f134aeb4d54933133368e8df2245e0c3\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在文档和话题中添加投票卡片，发布后就可以发起投票了。</span></p><h2 id=\"CoDbp\"></h2><h2 id=\"X3Odj\"><span class=\"ne-text\">插入投票卡片</span></h2><p id=\"ce310ba53a57971417d7413fd4c05b98\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"8r788\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过工具栏插入</span></h3><p id=\"671b0d7b7f9b488218e5eb48722b5bee\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">点击工具栏左上角的“特色卡片”按钮，在展开的下拉菜单中选中“投票”即可在当前光标位置插入一张投票卡片。</span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/21674429/1634181529251-c9269fa1-2c9b-459d-8064-268244edffac.png\" width=\"190\" id=\"u16a8c08f\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"e4f929b7aa13e9ee7908091c6b44a906\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"kKyRC\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过快捷键插入</span></h3><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"5ea21933a68da31230d97d2a103d03fd\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在文档编辑区域，按 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">/</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 可激活“快速插入卡片”；</span></li></ol><p id=\"3c5a3eb1ae58e9dc694d3aca648cef86\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/93503/1591070783484-b27199d2-6203-4ffc-a2af-0a7b348fa5c1.png\" width=\"1253\" id=\"TlmQ8\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"7128a86401eddfa9f7cf051b3c962ecc\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"35b84cfdb757f539eecac2ee68ce23b9\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ol start=\"2\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"4542569b3ccc170a17947d5bd7f44f3f\"><span class=\"ne-text\">输入投票卡片的中文（/投票）、全拼（/toupiao）、拼音首字母（/tp）或英文（/vote）来快速搜索卡片；</span></li></ol><p id=\"fcc27b847327717a907243f1d4811253\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/93503/1591070827053-9dfe5a67-b23e-45fb-8cb9-0e499ac806c1.png\" width=\"1248\" id=\"O65MS\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"6832ba8777ae8673b681e2e6ce8d7f48\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><ol start=\"3\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"b55538d65977a52e5ad3cbe69c6aedc6\"><span class=\"ne-text\">选择“投票”，即可在当前位置插入投票卡片。</span></li></ol><p id=\"91ac10ff80368569f4e22ddf00818e1e\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"733fdb79727cfc20c16cbe4f154160de\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"Wr7tZ\"></h2><h2 id=\"5U06Q\"><span class=\"ne-text\">编辑投票卡片</span></h2><p id=\"609ac822e5ba5e88a946598f0c84b60e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">新插入的投票如下所示：</span></p><p id=\"de92b09919dc6ce6a137e4185bb83ff2\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591068270298-4ed80fe8-74e4-403b-82ed-51494fdc906c.png\" width=\"850\" id=\"DTEfW\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"dd59d40873bd6938d58bce620ce31d66\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"E2s3N\"><span class=\"ne-text\">投票类型</span></h3><p id=\"77de4099a0dbebe936cc431dda86e4cd\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">支持两种类型的投票：一种是“单选”，投票人只能选择一个选项；另一种是多选，投票人可以同时选择多个选项。</span><span class=\"ne-text\">投票类型可以通过下图所示的下拉菜单进行设置：<br /></span><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591068396781-9cc2aebf-c9bf-4162-9381-5c624f6c2f01.png\" width=\"855\" id=\"qnxHX\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"2d3b99c156c12239f306d16a1af21ecf\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"638d3dd5e042e7836b4bd78e2590a16a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"ty8W5\"><span class=\"ne-text\">投票标题</span></h3><p id=\"7dbc88b598e3906156e66339cffab13f\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">投票的标题可以通过“投票类型”旁边的输入框进行输入，如下图所示：</span></p><p id=\"0748d52f92ffa5c3c554628dce67c64d\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591068469005-f629ff26-a2d3-44ca-afb9-21ff40577ca5.png\" width=\"839\" id=\"ukS0a\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"f939f7593d9f3f06adbe821f1fc83ae5\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"133715383a27e4c8937db9810b978967\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h3 id=\"QpMAS\"><span class=\"ne-text\">投票项</span></h3><div class=\"ne-quote\"><p id=\"e8dff07e9a4d99274fd4e78e298d4202\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #F5222D\">注意：每个投票</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #F5222D\">最少包含</span></strong><strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #F5222D\">两个</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #F5222D\">投票项。</span></p></div><p id=\"a2ddec96eb393148beb7f9744458003a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\">可通过修改对应投票项的内容来修改投票项的文案，也可以通过 “添加选项” 来增加投票项的个数，当投票项的个数大于 2 时，才会出现删除按钮，如下图所示：</span></p><p id=\"c3bd0725544d247974788a255571e440\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591068629100-5ccd80fa-b9cf-44aa-b117-4d553119378c.png\" width=\"836\" id=\"KTlPq\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"f7f8ec83537eadc52fe129dd1d6c793b\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: #000000\"></span></p><h3 id=\"l54OE\"><span class=\"ne-text\">投票截止时间</span></h3><p id=\"8920b0402f2ca43af9f07d92da81b516\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">新建的投票卡片，默认截止时间是第三天的凌晨；支持修改截止日期和时间，</span><span class=\"ne-text\">发布投票卡片前请检查截止时间是否符合预期。</span></p><p id=\"5b87e842e035183b5d1a8e055bfc0e3a\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"c8ab9b2d30c99f60a8d669cbe073e5cc\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591068822587-3fd4625f-86c4-43c8-b050-c43684fb261e.png\" width=\"529\" id=\"n502L\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"60d4c5f3b667cb51f514cb1b2e6e1257\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"0c04920e75c35ba9460bf9ad8eb292a2\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591068857683-117a830c-82ea-41c2-925d-d7942497f8cd.png\" width=\"495\" id=\"pLQba\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"1d3b4a3a1c04b102cdfc71b9076aebb3\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"1176566e4ad11b09af87e370e683a5cd\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"ptYwY\"><span class=\"ne-text\">发布投票卡片</span></h2><p id=\"3e1ae5fe89a74682f15ac3fa92e0c903\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">完成投票的创建之后，可以通过发布文档的方式来发布投票。</span></p><p id=\"3196e3e9b3b77f78e39f6328e21ac5c8\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591068943801-3019ea2b-7692-4f7f-9e1d-69a2edbdcd03.png\" width=\"1188\" id=\"TfghM\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"f469d597faf513ee79b284a19240c793\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"de25dfc74346a594ccceb804628157e6\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"1d431cc73a5331fa8909e98411b72222\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><h2 id=\"MVMQt\"><span class=\"ne-text\">参与投票</span></h2><p id=\"4d001339bb0b2728e3e114635d7b8233\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">投票发布之后，参与者打开文章后，看到的投票卡片如下图所示：</span></p><p id=\"15d5c6ed7565a20d362f474a84a86cf9\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591069043738-34b34d5a-1c37-4c87-b686-cf27ec9d0308.png\" width=\"789\" id=\"lFPQ3\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"320ab56f855e8248f377260619375c21\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">当投票人选中了投票项之后，“投票”按钮将变为可点击状态，点击“投票”按钮即完成投票。此时，投票人将看到投票结果，如下图所示：</span></p><p id=\"3afb50ad6025f85cb895e56c9fb0dff2\" class=\"ne-p\"><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/405557/1591069144939-6dae7d14-75e8-4060-b332-be21ce704e40.png\" width=\"806\" id=\"VRBDO\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"321e8efa82ae58eda3039a655fcdcccf\" class=\"ne-p\"><br></p><p id=\"1bd7567911ca5925e015dbbf68f5736a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在投票</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">截止之前</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">，已经投票的投票人可以通过点击“重新投票”按钮来重新投票，点击“重新投票”按钮后的投票流程和第一次投票的流程是一样的。</span></p><p id=\"u0251639a\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ub83a3158\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\"></span></p><p id=\"ua5fedbce\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\" style=\"color: rgb(23, 26, 29)\">如果对语雀有任何的建议或意见，可以提交反馈：</span><a href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" data-href=\"https://www.yuque.com/feedbacks/new\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">语雀反馈通道 </span></a><span class=\"ne-text\">  感谢你的支持！</span></p></div>",
